When we need to add some text inside the app, we should use the translation.json file to add the text.
We should use the i18next library to translate the text.
We should use the react-i18next library to translate the text.
We should use the i18next-resources-to-backend plugin to load the translations from the translation.json file.
We should use the i18next-browser-languagedetector plugin to detect the language of the user.
